/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: mps_OPSTINA_NASELJE */
/*==============================================================*/
create table mps_OPSTINA_NASELJE
(
DR_IDENTIFIKATOR char(3) not null,
OP_OZNAKA numeric(5,0) not null,
MPS_DR_IDENTIFIKATOR char(3) not null,
NM_DENTIFIKATOR integer not null,
constraint PK_MPS_OPSTINA_NASELJE primary key clustered (MPS_DR_IDENTIFIKATOR, DR_IDENTIFIKATOR, OP_OZNAKA, NM_DENTIFIKATOR)
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: MPS_OPSTINA_NASELJE_PK */
/*==============================================================*/
create unique clustered index MPS_OPSTINA_NASELJE_PK on mps_OPSTINA_NASELJE (
MPS_DR_IDENTIFIKATOR ASC,
DR_IDENTIFIKATOR ASC,
OP_OZNAKA ASC,
NM_DENTIFIKATOR ASC
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: OPSTINA_NASELJE_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index OPSTINA_NASELJE_FK on mps_OPSTINA_NASELJE (
DR_IDENTIFIKATOR ASC,
OP_OZNAKA ASC
);

/*==============================================================*/
/* Index: OPSTINA_NASELJE2_FK */
/*==============================================================*/
create index OPSTINA_NASELJE2_FK on mps_OPSTINA_NASELJE (
MPS_DR_IDENTIFIKATOR ASC,
NM_DENTIFIKATOR ASC
);

alter table mps_OPSTINA_NASELJE
add constraint FK_MPS_OPST_OPSTINA_N_MPS_OPST foreign key (DR_IDENTIFIKATOR, OP_OZNAKA)
references MPS_OPSTINA (DR_IDENTIFIKATOR, OP_OZNAKA)
on update restrict
on delete restrict;

alter table mps_OPSTINA_NASELJE

on update restrict
on delete restrict;
